      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under CPB-representative operating conditions (flow rates 3.0–5.5 L/min, rotational speeds 2800–3500 RPM, blood analog fluid at 37°C). The validation domain overlaps substantially with the COU operating envelope. Geometric similarity is exact (same CAD geometry). Fluid similarity is high (blood analog viscosity matched to within 5% of clinical blood viscosity). Gradation 2 achieved.",
